Adakah kerana
alam semesta tidak terhingga?

71
00:04:26,992 --> 00:04:28,946
Tepat sekali.

72
00:04:30,222 --> 00:04:31,222
Jangan risau, Jay.

73
00:04:39,164 --> 00:04:40,164
Jika Angelo mengetahui tentang kami,

74
00:04:41,024 --> 00:04:42,609
Saya akan bercakap dengannya.

75
00:04:43,264 --> 00:04:44,264
Walaupun ia berakhir dengan penumbuk.

76
00:04:45,085 --> 00:04:47,921
Saya sayang awak, Jay.

77
00:04:52,494 --> 00:04:53,494
Sehingga saintis menemui
akhir alam semesta.

78
